Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Therefore there's not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.62,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,因此 这里没有足够的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:08.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,if you took all the oceans on the earth and converted it to rocket propellant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:08.10,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,如果你把地球上所有的海洋转化为火箭推进剂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.44,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and then shipped it up to the moon
